                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39384489/" class="">第165页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/89829692/" class=" " title="▁ ▂ ▃ ▄ ▅">▁ ▂ ▃ ▄ ▅</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39384489">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39384489/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p39384489-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 
其实这与马克思的非进化论式的历史观并不冲突。马林诺斯基提供的材料对原始黄金社会的史学幻想确是立破的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-09-28 10:25</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p39384489-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
其实这与马克思的非进化论式的历史观并不冲突。马林诺斯基提供的材料对原始黄金社会的史学幻想确是立破的。
